    {
      "id": "n1",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 0,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "About the Section"
    },
    {
      "id": "n2",
      "type": "image",
      "order": 1,
      "src": "https://deutsch-pruefung.de/_next/image?url=%2Fsection-assets%2Fbear-mascot.webp&w=384&q=75",
      "alt": "Study bear mascot"
    },
    {
      "id": "n3",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 2,
      "text": "The Sprechen (Speaking) module at B1 level takes approximately 15 minutes and includes three communicative tasks with your partner and the examiners."
    },
    {
      "id": "n4",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 3,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 1: Gemeinsam etwas planen (Planning Together)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n5",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 4,
      "text": "• Plan an activity together with your partner (e.g., DVD evening, birthday party, trip)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n6",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 5,
      "text": "• Discuss the given points and make suggestions (Vorschläge machen)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n7",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 6,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 2: Ein Thema präsentieren (Present a Topic)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n8",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 7,
      "text": "• Present a current topic using 5 slides (Folien)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n9",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 8,
      "text": "• Slides: Introduction, Personal Experience, Home Country, Pros & Cons with Opinion, Conclusion"
    },
    {
      "id": "n10",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 9,
      "level": 4,
      "text": "Teil 3: Über ein Thema sprechen (Discuss a Topic)"
    },
    {
      "id": "n11",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 10,
      "text": "• Respond to questions from examiners and your partner about your presentation"
    },
    {
      "id": "n12",
      "type": "paragraph",
      "order": 11,
      "text": "• Give your partner feedback (Rückmeldung) on their presentation"
    },
    {
      "id": "n13",
      "type": "heading",
      "order": 12,
      "level": 3,
      "text": "Teil 1 - Gemeinsam etwas planen (Planning Together)"
